<title>UK: Securicor sees H1 loss at comms division.</title>
<headline>Securicor sees H1 loss at comms division.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-03-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Diversified security group Securicor Group Plc said on Thursday that its communications division is likely to record operating losses of around nine million stg in the half year to March 31, 1997.</p>
